
13,01* flux's second small ansi totorial - from outlines to shading                 

06,01      04 06hi! i was making a little logo couple of days ago,  and i saved the file 
06,01after each steps. the logo was "last". somethings have to be clear first..

15,01 06a) i am not making this "tutorial" to tell you *how* to draw, just telling you
15,01    06my way to draw, because i think i have at least some experience
06,01 b) the result is not free, it's for my own use

06,01think i'll begin.15 06ehrm..


